{
  "texts": [
    "The corresponding full story is presented in Appendix C.",
    "Human participant evaluation has been generally held as the gold-standard evaluation technique for creative language generation tasks such as story generation (Celikyilmaz et al., 2020; Caglayan et al., 2020; van der Lee et al., 2021).",
    "To extensively evaluate our method, we design three human participant studies.",
    "In the first, participants are asked to judge the goodness of the stories we generate and compare stories generated by our technique against those generated by the baseline method.",
    "The comparisons are based on multiple evaluation criteria."
  ]
}